channel.title: Cannot see my computer now?
channel.description: Yesterday I had someone set me all up... He had server running on my pc... I turned it off lastnight, and I am on now, and it is saying "Error: I Can NOT see your service on port 5555" I turned the router off last night, does that mean it reset possably?
